# Premium Maid Service: v1 scope

This is a **lead-generation marketing site** for a Delhi NCR domestic-help agency. Primary goal: enquiries via form, call, or WhatsApp.

## In scope (v1)

- Single-page marketing site (optional `/privacy-policy`, `/services`)
- English-only copy
- Booking/enquiry form (no backend required: Formspree/Web3Forms/WhatsApp)
- Sticky Call + WhatsApp CTAs on mobile
- Local SEO (meta tags, LocalBusiness schema)

## Out of scope: do not build unless client explicitly expands scope

- User accounts, login, auth
- Online payments
- Maid profile database or search
- Admin dashboard or CMS
- Mobile app
- Chatbot

## Tech defaults (from brief)

- Framework: Next.js or Astro
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Hosting: Vercel or Netlify

When unsure, read `docs/PROJECT_BRIEF.md` before adding features.
